## **1. Project Overview**  
**Project Name:** Multi-Language Restaurant Menu Website  
**Scope:**  
- Frontend-only React application (Vite + Tailwind CSS + Redux).  
- JSON-based data storage (no backend server).  
- Multi-language support (English, French, Spanish, Arabic).  
- QR code order tracking system.  
- Responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop).  
- Cloudinary integration for image management.  
- Domain registration and static hosting.  

